
After everything that happened to Kitty and Ian, there lives have finally settled to being normal again, Kitty is a singer, Ian is now an actor, Allison is married to Scott and they have an amazing baby boy named John O'Brien, Jordan is 11 years old, and Anthony had an unfortunate accident. The work has been turned upside down, flipped over, and put in a blender, but finally it's able to be something else, something better, or so thought. After Kitty isn't exactly Kitty anymore, Ian decides to seek help. Could he kill this monster or will his wife be gone forever?